data.description: Come see this 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home sitting on almost a full acree in Covington. Walk in to see beautiful vinyl flooring and your formal dining room with judges paneling. Enjoy preparing family meals in your kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, walk-in pantry, breakfast area, and island with breakfast bar opening to the family room. Spacious primary suite showcases tray ceiling, walk-in closet, double vanity, and a soaking tub. Open concept and large back patio with gazebo make this property great for entertaining family and friends. Fenced backyard is ready for your kids or pets. Ask how you can receive up to $1500 credit by using one of our preferred lenders. Exclusions may apply.  If we show your buyer, your buyer broker commission is reduced to 1.25% PER our listing agreement.
